name: Lawrence DABNEY, Petitioner v. COURT OF COMMON PLEAS OF PHILADELPHIA COUNTY, Respondent
name_abbreviation: Dabney v. Court of Common Pleas

parties: Lawrence DABNEY, Petitioner v. COURT OF COMMON PLEAS OF PHILADELPHIA COUNTY, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 2nd day of March, 2011, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED. As Petitioner has a motion for return of bail pending before the trial court, the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
